OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with some mostly light
OL,6,Frain at times, though parts of the
OL,7,Feast coast will stay dry. Some heavier
OL,8,Frain will spread to the Trossachs
OL,9,Ftowards evening. Strengthening
OL,10,Fsoutherly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FHeavy rain will sweep east
OL,13,Facross the region this evening
OL,14,Faccompanied by strong to gale south or
OL,15,Fsouthwest winds. Clearer for a time
OL,16,Ftonight then blustery showers setting
OL,17,Fin.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
