OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA rather cloudy start with
OL,6,Ffrequent blustery showers and gale
OL,7,Fforce winds. A brighter afternoon with
OL,8,Fsome sunny intervals but still some
OL,9,Fshowers. Best sunshine in Angus. Winds
OL,10,Fslowly easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FEarly
OL,13,Frain then blustery showers on
OL,14,FThursday, gales. Colder with sunshine
OL,15,Fand showers on Friday, snow on high
OL,16,Fground. Remaining showery on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
